	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia Christi tecum.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Epistolam tuam una cum duabus declamationibus per <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioannem Fabritium</persName>, virum pietate et eruditione eximium, accepi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ago tibi gratias immortales, vir doctissime, atque ut vellem, ita optarem, ut et possem id tibi cumulatius referre.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Stipendiarii duo a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l280" cert="high">Lausanensibus</placeName> revocati in obscuro carcere philosophantur iam biduo vescentes pane hordeaceo et potantes aquam ob plura commissa.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cras forte liberati stabunt in duro examine procerum; postea <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tubingam</placeName> <persName ref="p1055" cert="high">Martino Frechto</persName> ex principis iussu commendabuntur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Maluissem vestrę theologię, imo syncerioris quam illic a quibusdam tractatur, futuros auditores; sed sententia procerum ducatus pręvaluit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Missa rursum abrogabitur in tota ditione <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtembergensi</placeName>, ut facile intelligis, ex schedula et autographo principis, quod litteris nuper kalendis septembris datis<note type="margin">a.R.: datas!</note> inclusit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri nobilis noster pręfectus retulit esse abrogatam, sed quo modo vel ratione, ignoro; quodsi rescivero, te certiorem fatiam.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Princeps lavat in thermis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l195" cert="high">Geppingensibus</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsaris</persName> profectionem ad <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratenses</placeName>, quam habeo ex doctore <persName type="auto_name">Paulo Helio</persName>, qui hic agit vindemiam, ad te nunc dedi.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si ex <persName ref="p8374" cert="high">Hedione</persName> plura, cui ob id scripsi, recepero, id et tibi communicabo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesar</persName> non est procul a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2345" cert="high">Keisersluther</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuunt, ne in <placeName ref="l632" cert="high">Alsatia</placeName>, si a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> fugatus fuerit, hybernet; reliquę enim provintię propemodum omnes sunt exhaustę.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fiat domini voluntas; merentur enim ista peccata nostra et impoenitentia.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O bone deus, serva ecclesiam Christi etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l411" cert="high">Richenvillę</placeName> 27. septembris 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] ex animo <persName ref="p1010" cert="high">Matthias Erbius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eximio viro pietate et eruditione d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, theologo et antistiti ecclesię <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName>, domino suo semper observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
